Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.67,0:00:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.06,0:00:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.23,0:00:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.11,0:00:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.28,0:00:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.48,0:00:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.25,0:00:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.00,0:00:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.20,0:01:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.18,0:01:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代要當老師啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得無法想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.01,0:02:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好喔,女子高中的老師\N我也想去當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.55,0:02:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以跟學生亂來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.35,0:02:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,你能勝任嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.45,0:02:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不關你們的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要吵我啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.32,0:02:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎喲,老師\N不要這樣不通人情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.39,0:02:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊,愛生氣的老師\N會馬上被學生討厭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.76,0:02:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不要再鬧了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.93,0:02:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.17,0:02:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代明天開始要去教學實習了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.97,0:02:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們在給他加油打氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.24,0:02:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.24,0:02:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來只是像在吵他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.45,0:02:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,他這次要去的高中\N聽說是妳的母校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.62,0:02:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說\N是妳老公以前教書的學校囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.49,0:02:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.96,0:02:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\N鄉下高中的實習被拒絕了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.27,0:03:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,我申請書太晚提出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.21,0:03:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來想辦法幫你講講看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.14,0:03:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管包在我身上,惣一郎也是\N我把他弄進去當講師的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.36,0:03:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無爺爺在當理事的學校…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高中女生,高中女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.96,0:03:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-好耶,好耶…\N-高中女生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.50,0:03:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去管理員和她老公\N相遇的女子高中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.77,0:03:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去當實習老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.78,0:03:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#53高中女生威力爆發\N對響子發出愛的宣戰佈告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.03,0:04:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.96,0:04:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.43,0:04:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不要緊吧\N你們整晚都沒讓他睡,不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.24,0:04:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的啦,他還年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.14,0:04:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要讓高中女生乖乖聽話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.45,0:04:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是很需要體力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.16,0:04:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我姓音無,從今天起\N擔任各位的地質學老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真討厭,怎麼來個老頭子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.30,0:04:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就沒有年輕一點的老師嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-真討厭\N-就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來好溫和的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他應付得來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師,你有女朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.84,0:04:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,我不太有女人緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.45,0:04:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他真的回答了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳真壞\N居然問了妳明明知道的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.86,0:05:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,我們開始上課吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.97,0:05:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,大家安靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.54,0:05:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.64,0:05:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用客氣,因為我是班長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.71,0:05:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師,我們班就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.75,0:05:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最好大聲一點比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.65,0:05:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,以後我會注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.40,0:05:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都沒有老師的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.85,0:06:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來介紹從今天起\N負責二年四班的實習老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.63,0:06:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位同學安靜點,安靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.47,0:06:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代老師,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.55,0:06:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位同學…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.66,0:06:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我叫五代裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從今天起兩個禮拜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.13,0:06:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,大家安靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.61,0:07:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用客氣,因為我是班長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,她是班長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長得好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.62,0:07:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從今天開始\N由我擔任各位的國文老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.23,0:07:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有問題!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.30,0:07:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師,你有沒有女朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安靜點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼吵,老師怎麼回答呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安靜點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.31,0:07:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師,到底有沒有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.34,0:07:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前可以稱得上是女朋友的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.31,0:07:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該怎麼說才好呢,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然認真想了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.40,0:08:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上課態度\N最好再嚴謹一點比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.10,0:08:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,因為被學生的氣勢壓倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這裡男老師很少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.47,0:08:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家覺得很稀奇\N所以才會在那裡瞎起閧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.52,0:08:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來好像很專情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.46,0:08:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點憔悴的感覺蠻不錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.79,0:08:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一種憂鬱的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.50,0:08:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才不叫憂鬱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.67,0:08:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是單純的死氣沈沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.44,0:08:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,到底在想什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.07,0:08:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在女子高中裡\N這種事很平常嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是因為男生很少的關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.25,0:08:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以管理員才會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.72,0:08:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎究竟是個怎麼樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.66,0:08:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢業紀念冊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.23,0:09:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的照片蠻多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能很出鋒頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.13,0:09:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對,我是來看她老公的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來今年又沒指望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.07,0:09:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來我們學校的男老師\N大多都是軟弱型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.98,0:09:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊\N難道就沒有堅毅一點的男人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.85,0:09:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八神,妳幫忙去拿\N下一節課要用的幻燈片好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.09,0:10:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.46,0:10:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.26,0:10:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,講師還真多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.01,0:10:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫值日生去拿不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在這麼暗的地方做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.74,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.14,0:10:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼老是在意已經死掉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰死掉了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.99,0:11:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,放鬆的話會想睡覺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.22,0:11:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼淚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.22,0:11:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是打哈欠流出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.19,0:11:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我昨天沒有睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳從剛才就在了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.67,0:11:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.97,0:11:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事不要講出去好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.21,0:12:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,就當作我們兩人的祕密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著畢業紀念冊落淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.26,0:12:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的女朋友死掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而她是這裡的畢業生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.96,0:12:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪他會顯得有點憂鬱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八神,妳是認真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.82,0:12:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不是對他沒興趣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.02,0:12:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳還說他只是單純的死氣沈沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.75,0:12:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人的價值觀是會變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.46,0:12:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,價值觀啊,居然持續不到半天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.06,0:12:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.03,0:13:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧,妳就好好加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.47,0:13:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當然會加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.48,0:13:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.32,0:13:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請打起精神來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.62,0:13:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.23,0:13:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛喔,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.70,0:14:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種惡作劇\N永遠都不會過時的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.47,0:14:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,妳看妳看\N是音無老師唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.14,0:14:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點的話,他就要走了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.18,0:14:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,快去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.15,0:14:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-響子,妳真是沒勇氣\N-膽小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.72,0:14:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候真的很孩子氣\N居然想用那種方式來表達愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.84,0:14:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,是哪個女孩印上去的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.28,0:14:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那時候開始\N我就常常去找老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.68,0:14:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是老師常常不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨著我跟老師見面的次數增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.92,0:15:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我變得更加頻繁地去找老師了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來,高田同學繼續唸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.56,0:15:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.10,0:15:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是老師對我的態度\N不論是第一次跟我打招呼時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是比較熟了以後\N都感覺不到有什麼改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.91,0:15:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼搞的,她怎麼一直看著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.48,0:15:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時候會安靜到覺得很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.72,0:15:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始我覺得老師有種\N很難靠近的氣氛,然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.83,0:15:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託,妳真的是認真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.20,0:15:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳喜歡那種沈悶的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是沈悶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.11,0:15:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是在承受一段痛苦的過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.91,0:15:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.04,0:15:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼是痛苦的過去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問那麼多幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.38,0:16:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,八神\N如果妳真的想跟他交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.12,0:16:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不趁教學實習這段期間\N把他搞定的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.72,0:16:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後就沒機會了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.76,0:16:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.50,0:16:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望能永遠在他身邊\N幫他加油打氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要回家了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,你們也要回家了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.86,0:16:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,我們陪你走一段路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.81,0:16:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天啊,這是木造出租公寓耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.91,0:17:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在居然還有這種房子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.15,0:17:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是你班上的學生嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.29,0:17:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟學生的感情不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.59,0:17:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,不是這樣的\N是他們硬要到這裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.26,0:17:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人是誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是這裡的房客吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之,請他們上去坐坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.51,0:17:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼好可不可以的\N那是你的房間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.91,0:17:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說…說得也是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.95,0:17:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代老師幹嘛畏畏縮縮的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.09,0:17:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家要不要上來坐一坐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇,真的可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.89,0:17:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.73,0:18:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代幹嘛畏畏縮縮的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進來吧,房間裡有點凌亂\N大家隨便坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.81,0:18:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點凌亂?\N根本什麼都沒有嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.25,0:18:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個房間無色無味,好單調喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.55,0:18:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女…女高中生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.16,0:18:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蛇男!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師,他是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以看他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.79,0:18:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,今天是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.23,0:18:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你一直想把我排擠在外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.03,0:18:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是過來打個招呼而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.10,0:18:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平時謝謝你們照顧五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.81,0:18:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就像五代的大哥一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.21,0:18:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,真的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.88,0:18:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有我的話\N他什麼事都辦不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.82,0:18:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你不要胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.45,0:18:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝果汁好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.72,0:18:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是五代班上的學生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.26,0:19:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一天就把學生帶回家\N老師,你還真行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.86,0:19:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.90,0:19:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女的是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.97,0:19:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好性感喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.07,0:19:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好挑逗喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師,不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.57,0:19:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼不要緊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,請喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.27,0:19:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很不好意思,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.98,0:19:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,她是管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼他要這樣畢恭畢敬的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.92,0:19:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,五代\N這件白襯衫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面有個紅心的那件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經把它洗乾淨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.70,0:19:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住在這棟公寓裡\N管理員還會幫房客洗衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.04,0:19:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的,只有五代特別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.97,0:19:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她總是特別偏護五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.44,0:19:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,我才沒有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.11,0:19:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡的管理員只有妳一個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳有老公吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.95,0:19:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是寡婦,寡婦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寡婦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.37,0:20:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寡婦的意思就是單身吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.47,0:20:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,的確可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.17,0:20:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寡婦和房客,這種情況蠻常見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.94,0:20:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然還幫他洗衣服\N關係一定不尋常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們一定上過床了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,上過床了,上過床了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.29,0:20:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八神,怎麼辦?\N妳要放棄嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為什麼要放棄?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.72,0:20:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上過床也只是你們在說而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.63,0:20:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.06,0:20:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題在於五代老師的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.73,0:20:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況對方是個寡婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.93,0:20:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高中女生一定比寡婦更有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.64,0:20:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.94,0:20:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼時候規定的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.57,0:20:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不管呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.11,0:20:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個臭女人,居然把我特地\N印上去的紅心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託啦,求求你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.37,0:21:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果成功的話\N你們要吃什麼我都請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.34,0:21:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望能掌握這一瞬間的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.02,0:21:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.52,0:21:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.29,0:21:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有點事想跟你談談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.79,0:21:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.26,0:21:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.87,0:21:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼說,沒能好好招待你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.24,0:21:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還有一堆怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.01,0:22:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跑到你家去,你有生氣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.95,0:22:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啊,我覺得很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.22,0:22:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-真的嗎?\N-真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.65,0:22:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.17,0:22:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拍到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.84,0:22:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拍得很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.21,0:22:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即可拍相機能拍成這樣\N算是很棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.47,0:22:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.61,0:22:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳拍這張照片要幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.21,0:22:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.88,0:22:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,限時信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.45,0:22:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.89,0:22:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,是寄給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.86,0:22:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會是什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.10,0:23:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.87,0:23:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向我宣戰…是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.88,0:23:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像上面所敘述的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.02,0:23:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作者追求著理想主義\N個人主義的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.39,0:23:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了後期,則發表了\N以人類自我中心為主的作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.90,0:23:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚年則是“則天去私”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.06,0:23:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是捨去自我\N試圖從大自然的角度來看待一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.74,0:23:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於擺脫了個人主義…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.65,0:23:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八神,妳怎麼穿成這個樣子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.65,0:23:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是被其他人看到的話\N後果會很嚴重的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.85,0:23:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就那麼沒有魅力嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.46,0:23:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.06,0:24:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『裸體進攻!\N五代招架不住的誘惑作戰!』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.43,0:24:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的女高中生真的很敢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.18,0:24:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.56,0:24:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.31,0:24:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.61,0:24:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.98,0:25:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.09,0:25:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.33,0:25:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.50,0:25:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.90,0:25:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢…濡濕而發光

